You are The Lovers

Motive, power, and action, arising from Inspiration and Impulse.

The Lovers represents intuition and inspiration. Very often a choice needs to be made.

Originally, this card was called just LOVE. And that's actually more apt than "Lovers." Love follows in this sequence of growth and maturity. And, coming after the Emperor, who is about control, it is a radical change in perspective. LOVE is a force that makes you choose and decide for reasons you often can't understand; it makes you surrender control to a higher power. And that is what this card is all about. Finding something or someone who is so much a part of yourself, so perfectly attuned to you and you to them, that you cannot, dare not resist. This card indicates that the you have or will come across a person, career, challenge or thing that you will fall in love with. You will know instinctively that you must have this, even if it means diverging from your chosen path. No matter the difficulties, without it you will never be complete.

Well after 7 years I bid Gilmore Girls Farewell. I have enjoyed coming home on Tuesday nights and watching Gilmore Girls with my mother and then discussing the show with her. Now tonight is the series finally.

Well I am at work by myself and having a hard time working. I had a nice Christams enjoyed watching the nieces and nephews open gifts. My New Years I spent with some friends relaxed playing board games and talking. I thought Dick Clark sounded and looked better this year than last year. It is nice to see him behind a desk working on NYE.

For 2007 I have one goal and that is to spend less and get out of debt. I have one bill almost paid off this makes me happy.

2012 Olympic Decision Announcement Party


Rockefeller Plaza will be the official viewing site for all Olympic decision day action! Beginning at 5:00pm on July 5th, New Yorkers will gather in Rockefeller Plaza to celebrate New York's Olympic Bid. The final presentations to the IOC will be shown on a Jumbotron all evening, with New York's presentation beginning at 10:30pm. The 2012 Olympic Decision Announcement will be shown live at 7:30am on July 6th. 



I hope NY gets the bid I would like to see a how NY handles that kind of a crowd that would be bigger than what they already have.
